    \"surface_strategy\": \"Grid Borders ('Technical' look). Containers with flat backgrounds and 1px borders. Sharp edges or max 4px radius (rounded-sm). Minimize soft shadows.\",
    \"padding\": \"Generous internal padding (p-6 or p-8) for main containers to ensure text does not collide with structural borders.\",
