  \"motion_and_interactions\": {
    \"hover_states\": \"All interactive elements MUST explicitly set text color on hover. Use subtle background darkening (e.g. hover:bg-gray-50) for interactive rows.\",
    \"transitions\": \"Use transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out for standard UI elements.\",
    \"loading\": \"Prioritize skeleton screens matching the grid layout over generic spinners.\"
  },
  \"accessibility\": {
    \"contrast\": \"Maintain 4.5:1 ratio for normal text. Rely on the stark monochrome base to automatically handle most contrast needs.\",
    \"focus\": \"All interactive elements must use focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#002FA7]/50 focus:ring-offset-1 focus:ring-offset-white.\",
    \"testing_attributes\": \"All interactive elements (buttons, inputs, tab triggers, kanban cards) MUST have a data-testid attribute formatted as kebab-case-role (e.g., data-testid='create-task-button').\"
  },
  \"instructions_to_main_agent\": [
    \"Strictly follow the Archetype 4 Light Theme color palette. Avoid arbitrary colors; use #002FA7 exclusively for primary actions and active states.\",
    \"Use pure HTML and Tailwind for structural layout (grid, flex) and heavily customize Shadcn components (strip out heavy radii and soft shadows, replacing with rounded-sm and 1px borders).\",
    \"Construct the app layout with a fixed left sidebar (w-64) and a sticky top header (h-16).\",
    \"The Project Dashboard must use the 'Control Room' grid (dense, cardless or flat 1px-bordered). Incorporate Shadcn charts or Recharts for progress metrics.\",
    \"The Tasks Kanban should be functional. Use columns with a distinct background (#F8F9FA) and crisp white cards inside.\",
    \"The Learning Portal code editor should emulate a technical IDE interface. You can use a dark theme specifically inside the code editor bounding box for realism, but the rest of the portal should remain light theme.\",
    \"The GitHub integration panel should present commits and PRs in a dense, scan-first list with monospace hashes.\",
    \"Never use generic default sans-serif for headings; ensure Outfit is configured in Tailwind and imported.\",
    \"Ensure every form and button includes data-testid.\"
  ]
}"
